\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3682/d3682034.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3682%2Fd3682034.gif&h=ffa97448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張元英鏡頭前表現相當成熟。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n有網友直言：「比起當初意識SOMI是國中生，張元英其實離國小畢業沒有很久這件事更驚人。」目前14歲的張元英正就讀國中二年級，在《PRODUCE 48》最終票選得到冠軍，因此成為限定團體IZ*ONE的C位成員，人氣和討論度都相當高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> MARK低左幾個愚樂台低汁會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n社會主義者佛利民<br />\n歐陽克<br />\nSonHyeJoo<br />\n通形百萬<br />\nNancyJewel我老婆<br />\n歌神張學友<br />\nIZ*ONCE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望以上會員反省下自己講過既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"做咩點我名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"#13<br />\nSonHyeJoo<br />\n4 日前<br />\n奶腳一晚都未奶得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e540c1dcf57d962b0b15e292790ea92e7b47f8","tid":896610,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5db3a327ab035518f9c4f594c4e6a4bf78549c7c","tid":896610,"uid":63057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"同元英做愛一定好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"想同你做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87879109f993d17cf6